{
  "stem": "747.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Later on, it saved my life, the gold watch, but not in that-- in that time, it was, it didn't mean anything, jewelry.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, let me-- I should tell you that while we were going out to work, we went in one way and the men and transport came in another way.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They went in a different direction.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We always had a chance, just-- just one word, one word, to call over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you hear?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you know?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe you heard of my father?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day a man answered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, I knew your father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who are you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the following day, I called back that my father's name was Elias.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The following day, he called me because that was it, just we passed by.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the SS was marching there, we couldn't talk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the following day he said, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to school with your father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the following day, an onion was flying over with-- and he called out this is for Judith [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Schwartz ?] from me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that night, we had a fantastic fiesta in our-- our-- I sliced up the onion, and everybody got a piece.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had a wonderful-- a wonderful feeling that we had something extra.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I met cousins of mine here and then an old friend there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And what was a very painful that-- in the beginning, end of July, about 5,000 Russian prisoner of war, young soldiers, were brought in to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They let them wear their uniform.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But every morning, they took them out for a walk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were marching, singing Russian songs, but I didn't understand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they were so lively.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were so young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were still not under nourished like we were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so brave and singing beautiful patriotic songs.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
